(HUMAN HEALTH AND NUTRITION: A COMPREHENSIVE GUIDE) Tj
T*
T*
(Introduction) Tj
T*
T*
(Human health is the foundation of individual well-being, societal productivity, and) Tj
T*
(quality of life. Nutrition  the process by which organisms obtain and use food for) Tj
T*
(energy, growth, and metabolic processes  is one of the most powerful determinants of) Tj
T*
(health outcomes. The relationship between what we eat and how our bodies function is) Tj
T*
(complex, deeply studied, and increasingly well understood.) Tj
T*
T*
(This guide covers the essential components of human nutrition, the physiology of major) Tj
T*
(body systems, common diseases and their prevention, mental health, the science of) Tj
T*
(exercise, and emerging frontiers in personalized medicine and longevity research.) Tj
T*
T*
