T*
T*
(- **Ghrelin**: "Hunger hormone" produced by stomach; stimulates appetite.) Tj
T*
T*
(- **Cortisol**: Stress hormone; promotes gluconeogenesis and fat storage \(especially) Tj
T*
(visceral\).) Tj
